query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_products,
  COUNT(DISTINCT brand) as total_brands,
  COUNT(DISTINCT partNumber) as unique_part_numbers,
  COUNT(DISTINCT productId) as unique_product_ids
FROM products;
